smetic bundle system\n-Added Halloween decor on vanilla maps (ends after October 31st)\n-Added warning pop-up when trying to access customize menu without a Wi-Fi connection\n-Added function to dismiss MOTD/NEWS and added a button restore MOTD to main menu\n-Adjusted texture memory optimizations \n-Adjusted item optimizations\n-Adjusted bomb sites in Carnival\n-Fixed minor prop issues in Santorini\n-Fixed bullets not being skinned properly by cosmetic \n-Fixed redundant dependency version checks\n-Fixed 3rd person recoil animations\n-Fixed issue with guns floating in the center of players\n-Fixed KOTH soviets getting the incorrect faction grenades\n-Fixed exploit in Autumn\n-Fixed a spot in Carnival that would result in the player getting stuck\n-Fixed physmats in Carnival that should not have bullet penetration\n\nModders\n-Added Vankrupt asset packs to download via modkit and create your own maps with\nhttps://mod.io/g/pavlov/u/vankrupt-games\n\nCommunity Server\n-Added the ability to record all matches as .replay files by adding \"bRecordReplays=true\" to their Game.ini (Pending Shack TV release)\n\nIn the near future it will be possible to watch these back via PavTV, Note: To playback matches with mods they will need to be uploaded to both PC and Oculus (with matching version numbers)", "created_date": 1729020484, "id": "8855749731103270", "version": "1.0.20", "version_code": 1619, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "8855636027781307"}, "asset_files": {"count": 2}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "2443267419018232", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8855749731103270"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created